# Info

Invoked to register special recipe serializers. Special recipes are dynamic recipes that can't be defined in JSON (like map cloning, firework crafting, etc.).

# Example

```js
ServerEvents.specialRecipeSerializers(event => {
	// Hide special recipe from recipe viewers
	event.ignoreSpecialRecipe('minecraft:crafting_special_armordye')
	
	// You can also register custom special recipes here
})
```
